generator client {
  provider = "prisma-client-js"
  output   = "../src/generated/prisma"
}

datasource db {
  provider = "postgresql"
  url      = env("DATABASE_URL")
}
```

Then also make sure your `.env` file at the project root has your database URL:
```
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://username:password@localhost:5432/yourdbname
```

Then run:
```
npx prisma generate